is \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":21367,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/12\/20\/cursing-believer-like-killing\/","url_meta":{"origin":43361,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Curses: Cursing a believer is like murdering him","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 20, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Mas\u2019ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cCursing a believer is like killing him.\u201d Source: al-Adab al-Mufrad lil-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 762 Grade: Sahih li ghayrihi (authentic due to external evidence) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u0646 \u0623\u0628\u064a \u0645\u0633\u0639\u0648\u062f \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0644\u064e\u0639\u0652\u0646\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32167,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/15\/sahaba-viewed-cursing-kabair\/","url_meta":{"origin":43361,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Curses: We viewed cursing brothers as major sin","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 15, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Yazid ibn Abi \u2018Ubayd reported: Salamah ibn al-Akwa\u2019, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cIf we saw a man curse his brother, we considered it as if he had come to a door of mortal sin.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Awsat\u0323 lil-T\u0323abara\u0304ni\u0304 6674 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u0646 \u064a\u064e\u0632\u0650\u064a\u062f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32176,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/15\/be-careful-what-you-curse-for\/","url_meta":{"origin":43361,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Cursing: Be careful what you curse for","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 15, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, was riding on a journey and a man cursed his she-camel. The Prophet said, \u201cWhere is the owner of the she-camel?\u201d The man said, \u201cIt is me.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cLeave her behind, for your curse has been answered.\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34162,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/04\/30\/do-not-insult-while-fasting\/","url_meta":{"origin":43361,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Siyam: Do not insult anyone while fasting","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 30, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cDo not insult anyone while you are fasting. If anyone insults you, then say: Indeed, I am fasting. If you are standing, then sit down.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Ibn Khuzaymah 1994 Grade: Hasan (fai